# 3D Surprise ❤️

An interactive 3D Valentine's experience featuring a parachute model with romantic message functionality.

![Preview](./Screenshot.png)

## Features ✨
- 🪂 Interactive 3D parachute model from Sketchfab
- 🎮 Orbit controls (rotate/zoom/pan)
- 🌈 Animated gradient background with "lightning" effect
- 💌 Toggleable love message with animations
- 📱 Responsive design for all devices
- ⏳ Loading screen with progress tracking
- 💖 Romantic styling with custom fonts and effects

## Live Demo 🚀
[View Live Demo](https://abdel-mars.io/3d-surprise/) 

